                  "emoji": "3Ô∏è‚É£",
                  "text": "<strong>Cacheable</strong> - Responses must define cacheability"
                },
                {
                  "emoji": "4Ô∏è‚É£",
                  "text": "<strong>Uniform Interface</strong> - Consistent API design"
                },
                {
                  "emoji": "5Ô∏è‚É£",
